The paper deals with the optimization of a communication system, which is a common topic in the Information Theory (cs.IT) and Communications (cs.COMM) sub-categories. The use of 1-bit quantization is a specific technique that falls under the Signal Processing (cs.SY) and Networking and Internet Architecture (cs.NI) sub-categories. Finally, the optimization of the system parameters to maximize a figure-of-merit involves machine learning and optimization techniques, which are also relevant to the Machine Learning (cs.LG) sub-category.
